WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Reading one candle.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.500
Before setups, read one candle.

00:06.500 --> 00:10.000
Every candle has four prices.

00:10.000 --> 00:16.500
Open, close, high, and low.

00:16.500 --> 00:21.000
The body is open to close.

00:21.000 --> 00:25.500
The wick is failed travel.

00:25.500 --> 00:30.500
Buyers finish stronger on a bullish close.

00:30.500 --> 00:35.500
Sellers finish stronger on a bearish close.

00:35.500 --> 00:38.500
A wick can poke and fail.

00:38.500 --> 00:41.500
The close is the truth.

00:41.500 --> 00:44.000
We do not act on a poke.

00:44.000 --> 00:47.000
Wait for the one-hour close.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
One candle is one sentence.

00:49.000 --> 00:49.700
Then run the checklist.
